[{"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f61d/6947/375_large.png?m=1658910399", "name": "go", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f61d/6947/375_normal.png?m=1658910399", "title": "Go 编程语言", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/go", "topics": 3155, "footer": "", "header": "Go 是一个开源的编程语言，它能让构造简单、可靠且高效的软件变得容易。", "title_alternative": "The Go Programming Language", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f61d/6947/375_mini.png?m=1658910399", "stars": 4031, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 375, "parent_node_name": "programming"}, "member": {"id": 719276, "username": "yuanyao", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/yuanyao", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b5f6/534f/719276_mini.png?m=1739240987", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b5f6/534f/719276_normal.png?m=1739240987", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b5f6/534f/719276_large.png?m=1739240987", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b5f6/534f/719276_xlarge.png?m=1739240987", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b5f6/534f/719276_xlarge.png?m=1739240987", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b5f6/534f/719276_xlarge.png?m=1739240987", "created": 1731139895, "last_modified": 1739240987}, "last_reply_by": "hunterster", "last_touched": 1740452747, "title": "最基础的 go 并发编程题，难倒了 90%的候选人", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1113786", "created": 1740369377, "deleted": 0, "content": "两个 goroutine 用 channel 通信，一个 goroutine 顺序发送 0,1,2,3,4 个数字，另一个 goroutine 接收并输出。\r\n考察了 goroutine 的控制、channel 的关闭等基础知识，面试者写的代码各种问题。\r\n\r\n1. 有的 goroutine 还没启动程序就退出了，提示后仍想不到使用 waitgroup ，context ，done channel 等手段，而是用 time sleep 等待；\r\n2. 有的 channel 不知道由生产者关闭，直接在主程序生产者还未发送结束就关闭结果 panic ；\r\n3. 有的不会检查消费者读关闭 channel 的返回值，程序直接死循环死锁。\r\n\r\n上周面试 5 个人只有 1 个人一次写出了执行没问题的代码，有 1 个经过提示也没写出来，剩下的能提示后逐步修改出正确的代码。\r\n\r\n这个题还是很经典的，不用问 GMP 、垃圾回收算法等八股文，这个题就能看出 go 基础了。", "content_rendered": "<p>两个 goroutine 用 channel 通信，一个 goroutine 顺序发送 0,1,2,3,4 个数字，另一个 goroutine 接收并输出。\n考察了 goroutine 的控制、channel 的关闭等基础知识，面试者写的代码各种问题。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>有的 goroutine 还没启动程序就退出了，提示后仍想不到使用 waitgroup ，context ，done channel 等手段，而是用 time sleep 等待；</li>\n<li>有的 channel 不知道由生产者关闭，直接在主程序生产者还未发送结束就关闭结果 panic ；</li>\n<li>有的不会检查消费者读关闭 channel 的返回值，程序直接死循环死锁。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>上周面试 5 个人只有 1 个人一次写出了执行没问题的代码，有 1 个经过提示也没写出来，剩下的能提示后逐步修改出正确的代码。</p>\n<p>这个题还是很经典的，不用问 GMP 、垃圾回收算法等八股文，这个题就能看出 go 基础了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1740369377, "replies": 87, "id": 1113786}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 7361, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 1726, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 389889, "username": "Salticey", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Salticey", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "cool", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c608/4947/389889_mini.png?m=1678550703", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c608/4947/389889_normal.png?m=1678550703", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c608/4947/389889_large.png?m=1678550703", "created": 1551858682, "last_modified": 1678550703}, "last_reply_by": "easynote", "last_touched": 1740453283, "title": "怎样克服入睡时对声音很敏感这件事", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1113983", "created": 1740444343, "deleted": 0, "content": "OP 睡觉时，但凡有点动静，比如握手楼对面有人讲话、风吹窗户的异响，都会打消我好不容易堆起来的睡觉。有时零点半躺床上睡觉能熬到三点都睡不着。最近连续一个月使用耳塞也导致耳道发炎了，感觉不能太依赖这玩意了😭😭😭😭", "content_rendered": "OP 睡觉时，但凡有点动静，比如握手楼对面有人讲话、风吹窗户的异响，都会打消我好不容易堆起来的睡觉。有时零点半躺床上睡觉能熬到三点都睡不着。最近连续一个月使用耳塞也导致耳道发炎了，感觉不能太依赖这玩意了😭😭😭😭", "last_mo